  <primary_category>Desserts</primary_category>
  <preparation>Cream sugar and margarine; add extracts and seeds.  Beat until creamy. Sift flour and baking powder and add to mixture.  Bake in a 375 degree oven until brown.  Remove from oven and cut into slats and turn on cut side.  Put back into oven to brown.</preparation>
